      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "This intermittent 500 error strongly suggests a resource or network instability issue under load. The `ECONNRESET` error during a Redis connection timeout points to the application losing its connection to the cache cluster. During peak traffic, your application might be overwhelming the Redis server or experiencing transient network hiccups between your service and the cache. You should investigate network latency to Redis and potentially implement more robust connection retry logic in your authentication middleware.",
