      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk, checked the load balancer and firewalls too and everything seems totally fine. it's just so hard to pin down because it's so unpredictable. it's like there's some hidden variable or something just messing with the packets. why would a connection just reset like that if everything on both ends says it's healthy?",
